about any other person

00:23:33.570 --> 00:23:36.320
at that chemistry
table, not one.

00:23:36.320 --> 00:23:40.022
The one man who could
hear, if what you are doing

00:23:40.022 --> 00:23:41.980
is not important or not
likely to be important,

00:23:41.980 --> 00:23:42.930
why are you doing it?

00:23:42.930 --> 00:23:47.020
The one man who could,
did become important.

