00:45:09.385 --> 00:45:11.260
AUDIENCE: Since you
asked for hard questions,

00:45:11.260 --> 00:45:13.430
which of your projects
did you enjoy the most?

00:45:13.430 --> 00:45:16.060
And which of them do you
think had the most impact?

00:45:16.060 --> 00:45:19.550
DAVID PATTERSON: Which
did I enjoy the most?

00:45:19.550 --> 00:45:21.270
Let me do the most impact.

00:45:21.270 --> 00:45:23.620
Because I'm kind of
wrapping things up,

00:45:23.620 --> 00:45:26.535
it's plausible RAID
had the biggest impact.

00:45:29.290 --> 00:45:31.520
Everybody uses it.

00:45:31.520 --> 00:45:35.455
The original RAID paper won
