It's a different group
with interdisciplinary mix

00:50:38.150 --> 00:50:38.710
and match.

00:50:38.710 --> 00:50:41.030
We tackle a problem.

00:50:41.030 --> 00:50:44.056
We've already visited you
guys on the next project

00:50:44.056 --> 00:50:45.180
to get some feedback on it.

00:50:45.180 --> 00:50:47.720
I don't know why more
people don't do it.

