You have to ask them.

00:50:49.020 --> 00:50:51.309
Why don't more people--
you should ask them.

00:50:51.309 --> 00:50:52.850
Why don't you guys
act like Berkeley?

00:50:52.850 --> 00:50:55.061
I'm sure they'd love that.

00:50:55.061 --> 00:50:57.515
There's probably a
nearby university.

